sentences: Dave Kane (born in Bangor, County Down, Northern Ireland) is a Double Bass player, composer and band leader.
Kane purchased an electric bass guitar from a local catholic priest for Â£50 when he was 16 years old.
Currently based in Leeds, Kane is a founder member of L.I.M.A. (Leeds improvised music association) and musical director/ composer for the L.I.M. A orchestra.
